data.description: Wonderfully updated Colonial with lots to offer in Enfield! This home features a spectacular and spacious Primary bedroom on the 2nd floor that you must see, featuring a grand vaulted ceiling, an updated full bath, and a nicely sized walk in closet. On the main floor you have a spacious updated kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and tile backsplash. The kitchen also features a slider to a large deck that overlooks a sprawling backyard that cleared and level which is great for children to play or backyard family gatherings. The remainder of the main level has a large dining room with another door to the backyard, a formal dining room, and 3 more bedrooms that have access to another full bath. Basement is also partially finished with drywall and a freshly painted cement floor to give additional bonus space for another hangout room, workout room, or perhaps a kids play area. Some other features include Central air, a newer furnace and water heater, and 200 amp electrical. Great location minutes from several restaurants, grocery stores, gas stations, shopping centers, and the highway. Come see and call this one your new home today!
